    "description": "The IMS3-SM is the module that contains the security manager present in the Dolby® IMS3000 (Product Model: CID1002) for hardware models IMS3-41, IMS3-42, IMS3-43, IMS3C-11, IMS3C-12, and IMS3C-13. The Dolby® IMS3000 can be hosted inside Digital Cinema DLP projectors (for hardware models IMS3-41, IMS3-42, and IMS3-43) or inside a LED display (for hardware models IMS3C-11, IMS3C-12, and IMS3C-13). It supports the highest JPEG-2000 decoding capabilities and also accepts alternative content.",
